* Simple\nSchedule
** How It Works
***_ Trigger type: Scheduled
***_ Schedule type: Simple
***_ Specify number + time unit
** Time Units
***_ Minutes
***_ Hours
***_ Days
***_ Weeks
** Limitations
***_ First run time: auto-assigned
***_ Minimum interval: 10 seconds
** When to Use
***_ Consistent recurring intervals
***_ No specific time requirement
